---
title: Chipotle Chicken and Savory Yellow Rice with Salsa Fresca and Spicy Lime Cream
description: Bowls have gone beyond “having a moment” and officially transformed into a dinnertime staple. And why not? They’re hearty, comforting, and so versatile. This version’s got kickin’ chicken served over a bed of savory turmeric rice, topped with fresh salsa and tangy chipotle-lime crema. Yep, this bodacious bowl is sure to satisfy.
